  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Caritas Zimbabwe Capacity Strengthening Program</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">An institutional  capacity strengthening grant to Caritas Zimbabwe National Office to enable it to achieve the following objectives;

Overall Objective: Caritas Zimbabwe is fully capacitated (human and financial resources) and relevant to addressing poverty and social exclusion to affected communities in Zimbabwe. 

Specific Objectives
1. Caritas Zimbabwe&#x2019;s coordination mechanism across its network is effective and relevant.
2. Caritas Zimbabwe is a resource centre to diocesan Caritas offices in research, documentation and information dissemination.
3. Caritas Zimbabwe is actively influencing policies and decision makers at sub-national, national and international level.</narrative>
  </description>
